Package Grupo11_ISCTE.Code_Smells_Detective

Class MethodEntity

java.lang.Object
Grupo11_ISCTE.Code_Smells_Detective.MethodEntity
public class MethodEntity
extends java.lang.Object
Represents the Method Entity. The method entity is a class that when instanced has the several fields of data present in the Excel file for a single method.
